FBIS4-23215 "drafr105_c_94002" FBIS-AFR-94-105 Daily Report 1 Jun 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA ANC Announces Closure of Washington Office ANC Announces Closure of Washington Office MB0106071594 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0500 GMT 1 Jun 94 MB0106071594 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] The ANC has announced the official closure of its office in the American capital, Washington, and says its affairs will be handled by the South Africa Embassy in future. In a statement ANC spokesman Madala Mthembu thanked Americans for their dependable partnership in the fight against apartheid. He said the task was now to rebuild South Africa to ensure economic and social upliftment.
